---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Notes on backend, DevOps, data, and AI automation from Robin Ward.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="page-hero section-border">
    <div class="wrap blog-hero">
        <p class="blog-eyebrow">Hexward Blog</p>
        <h1>Field Notes From Production</h1>
        <p class="blog-intro">Backend, DevOps, data, and AI automation notes from real client work, shipped systems, and the mistakes worth avoiding.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="wrap">
        {% if collections.posts.length %}
        <ul class="blog-list">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
            <li class="blog-list-item">
                <div class="blog-list-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
                <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
                {% if post.data.description %}<p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
                <a class="blog-list-link" href="{{ post.url }}">Read post &rarr;</a>
            </li>
        {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% else %}
        <div class="blog-empty">
            <h2>No posts yet</h2>
            <p>The feed is set up. The writing backlog is the only thing missing.</p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</section>
